text: Ropicomimus papuanus is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Breuning in 1940. It is known from Papua New Guinea.BioLib.cz - Ropicomimus papuanus. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Apomecynini Category:Beetles described in 1940
title: Ropicomimus papuanus
